digital-systems-engineering pack — content licence
===================================================

This pack is derived from:
    Towards Digital Engineering: The Advent of Digital Systems Engineering
    Jingwei Huang, Adrian Gheorghe, Holly Handley, Pilar Pazos, Ariel Pinto,
    Samuel Kovacic, Andrew Collins, Charles Keating, Andres Sousa-Poza,
    Ghaith Rabadi, Resit Unal, Teddy Cotter, Rafael Landaeta, Charles Daniels.
    Department of Engineering Management and Systems Engineering,
    Old Dominion University, Norfolk, VA, USA.
    arXiv:2002.11672 (2020); paper in press, Int. J. System of Systems Engineering.

Source licence: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
    (tier 2 — see ../../docs/SOURCE-VETTING.md)
No source-material download link is published (see ../../docs/LICENSING.md).
The pack is grounded only in the openly licensed arXiv preprint, NOT the
paywalled journal version.

