------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - ATTRIBUTION is satisfied: the authors and the work (title, arXiv:2002.11672,
    2020, Old Dominion University) are credited in PACK.yaml, in SKILL.md, and in
    every chapter file; this LICENSE links the CC BY 4.0 deed; and the chapters
