  - CHANGES INDICATED: this pack is a reference-depth paraphrase and synthesis,
    not a reproduction. It does not copy long verbatim passages of the source
    (verified mechanically by tools/check_overlap.py).
  - NO endorsement is implied. Nothing here suggests the authors or Old Dominion
