  - NO additional legal/technical restrictions are imposed beyond those of the
    underlying repository tooling licence.
  - Because CC BY 4.0 is neither non-commercial nor share-alike, this pack's
    content is NOT forced under CC BY 4.0; only the attribution obligation binds.

